<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/35.html" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt="永州阳明山杜鹃花海" title="永州阳明山杜鹃花海"/  src="/Article/UploadFiles/201612/2016121515441154.jpg" width=640 height=469></A> 杜鹃花海 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>
<P>永州阳明山万寿寺分布着数万亩映山红、鹿角杜鹃、云锦杜鹃、满山红、猴头杜鹃等高山野生杜鹃花，每年5月初前后，阳明山杜鹃花花期开放连成一片，誉为“天下第一杜鹃红”。&nbsp;&nbsp; <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/35.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A></P>
</div>
