<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/34.html" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt="永州阳明山万寿寺" title="永州阳明山万寿寺"/ src="/Article/wanshou/1.jpg" width=640 height=214></A>万寿寺 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>始建于宋、重修于明，万寿寺后有一古井，奉为“阳明圣水”。明嘉靖年间郑秀峰在此坐化成佛，明藩南渭王遂崇其号曰“七祖”，亲赐“名山千古仰，活佛万家朝”楹联。 <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/34.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A> 
</div>
</LI>
<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/33.html" target=_blank><IMG height=375 alt={$r[title]} src="/Article/UploadFiles/201701/2017010622554581.jpg" width=600 border=0></A><A title=红色之旅 href="/2012/0206/46916.html" target=_blank>红色之旅</A> 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1934年8月23日，红军在进行震惊中外的二万五千里长征中，由任弼时、王震、萧克率领红六军团8000多名官兵，翻过唐公庵，到达阳明山，在竹蒿芨一带消灭国民党一个保安团。&nbsp;&nbsp; <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/33.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A></P>
</div>
</LI>
<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/32.html" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt="永州阳明山春天美景" title="永州阳明山春天美景"/ src="/Article/UploadFiles/201701/2017010623123644.jpg" width=508 height=340></A> 灵山福地 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阳明山，一个阳光灿烂的名字。据《永州府志》载：“朝阳甫出，而山已明者，阳明山也……有银沙十里，鸟道盘折，上与天齐，其丽险绝，几疑无路，及登顶峰，左衡右嶷。&nbsp;&nbsp; <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/32.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A></P>
</div>
</LI>
<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/31.html" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt={$r[title]} src="/Article/UploadFiles/201202/20120215133948845.jpg" width=500 height=347></A>大黄江源瀑布群 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大黄江源瀑布群：位于阳明山大黄江源景区，瀑分五级，瀑与瀑间以潭相连，总长150米，最后一级，溪水从60米高处咆哮而下，如白蛟翻滚，气势磅礴，水声激越，声势夺人。&nbsp;&nbsp; <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/31.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A></P>
</div>
</LI>
<LI>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_2t><A href="/Article/jddy/30.html" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt={$r[title]} src="/Article/UploadFiles/201202/20120215133909747.jpg" width=508 height=762></A> 竹乡林海 
</div>
<div class=leftte1_1_2_3t><A title="{str_cut($r[title], 60)}" href="/{$r[url]}" target=_blank></A>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阳明山是野生动植物资源的宝库，森林覆盖率达到96%，拥有云豹、华南虎、南方红杉、华东黄杉等国家一、二级保护动植物101种，早在1982年就被列为湖南省重点自然保护区。&nbsp;&nbsp; <A class={$class} title="{str_cut($r[title], $titlelen ,'')}" href="/Article/jddy/30.html" target=_blank><FONT color=#cc0000>[详细]</FONT></A></P>
</div>
</LI></UL>
</div>
